panies listed at the above pages, and they will be able to help you with any questions regarding purchase, use and installation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To view the NHRA announcement in its entirety, visit <a href=\"http:\/\/www.nhraracer.com\">www.nhraracer.com<\/a> or click here: <a href=\"http:\/\/nhraracer.com\/content\/general.asp?articleid=71611&amp;zoneid=132\">NHRA 2020 Junior Dragster Announcement 09-11-19<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Today NHRA announced new safety requirements for their Junior Drag Racing League categories for the 2020 season. Racers in most classes will be required to wear a head and neck restraint device meeting SFI Spec 38.1 beginning June 1, 2020. And starting January 1, 2020, cars in<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4561","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-manufacturers"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4561","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4561"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4561\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4563,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4561\/revisions\/4563"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4561"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-jso